class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight text-gray-900\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Engineered for the <span class=\"gradient-text\">Future</span></h2><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Experience the perfect blend of performance, technology, and sustainability in every ride.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"\n                group relative p-8 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\n                md:col-span-2\n                bg-white/60\n                \n                border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg\n              \" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.9), rgba(255,255,255,0.6)), url(&#x27;https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620802051782-726fa6b3308d?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80&#x27;);background-size:cover;background-position:center;opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><div class=\"\n                    p-3 rounded-2xl w-fit mb-4\n                    bg-white shadow-sm\n                  \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-battery w-8 h-8 text-primary\"><rect width=\"16\" height=\"10\" x=\"2\" y=\"7\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"22\" x2=\"22\" y1=\"11\" y2=\"13\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900\">150km Range</h3><p class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">Go further with our advanced Lithium-ion battery technology designed for long commutes.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div><div class=\"\n                group relative p-8 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\n                md:col-span-1\n                bg-white border-primary/20 shadow-md\n                \n                border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg\n              \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><div class=\"\n                    p-3 rounded-2xl w-fit mb-4\n                    bg-secondary/10\n                  \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-8 h-8 text-secondary\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900\">Fast Charging</h3><p class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">0 to 80% in just 40 minutes.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div><div class=\"\n                group relative p-8 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\n                md:col-span-1\n                bg-white/60\n                \n                border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg\n              \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><div class=\"\n                    p-3 rounded-2xl w-fit mb-4\n                    bg-secondary/10\n                  \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-gauge w-8 h-8 text-primary\"><path d=\"m12 14 4-4\"></path><path d=\"M3.34 19a10 10 0 1 1 17.32 0\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900\">85 km/h</h3><p class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">Top speed that keeps you ahead of traffic.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div><div class=\"\n                group relative p-8 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\n                md:col-span-2\n                bg-white/60\n                bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50\n                border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg\n              \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><div class=\"\n                    p-3 rounded-2xl w-fit mb-4\n                    bg-white shadow-sm\n                  \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-smartphone w-8 h-8 text-blue-500\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"20\" x=\"5\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900\">Smart Connect</h3><p class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">Control your ride with our dedicated app.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div><div class=\"\n                group relative p-8 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\n                md:col-span-1\n                bg-white/60\n                \n                border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg\n              \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><div class=\"\n                    p-3 rounded-2xl w-fit mb-4\n                    bg-secondary/10\n                  \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-8 h-8 text-green-500\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900\">Advanced Safety</h3><p class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">CBS braking system and anti-theft alarm.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300\"></div></div><div class=\"\n                group relative p-8 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\n                md:col-span-2\n                bg-white/60\n                \n                border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg\n              \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><div class=\"\n                    p-3 rounded-2xl w-fit mb-4\n                    bg-secondary/10\n                  \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" c